'''飓风克里斯蒂'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Kristy}}）是[[2006年太平洋飓风季|2006年太平洋飓风季]]持续时间相比较长的一个[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]。系统于8月30日经墨西哥西南方向近海的[[东风波|东风波]]发展形成，然后迅速增强并升级成飓风，达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]130公里的最高强度。接下来由于[[海面温度|水温]]降低，同时东北方向的[[2006年飓风约翰|飓风约翰]]还令[[风切变|风切变]]增多，克里斯蒂逐渐减弱。受转向气流弱化影响，气旋转向南面飘移，于9月2日降级成热带低气压。

次日，克里斯蒂一度重新增强成热带风暴，但很快就再度弱化成热带低气压。转向西进后，风暴外部环境略朝有利于热带天气系统发展的方向转变，气旋因此第三度成为热带风暴，但由于外部环境又变得不利，系统最终于9月9日消散。克里斯蒂自始至终没有对陆地构成任何影响，<ref name="tcr">{{cite report | author = Lixion Avila | date = 2006-10-12 | title = Hurricane Kristy Tropical Cyclone Report | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130521105313/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-EP122006_Kristy.pdf | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2013-05-21 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-EP122006_Kristy.pdf | archivedate = 2013-05-21 | format = [[PDF|PDF]] }}</ref>只不过一度对[[克拉里翁岛|克拉里翁岛]]构成轻度威胁<ref>{{cite web | author1 = Rhome | author2 = Franklin | date = 2008-08-30 | title = Tropical Depression Twelve-E Wind Speed Probabilities Number One | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-11 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.wndprb.001.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151006055409/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.wndprb.001.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-10-06 }}</ref>。此外在[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]位于[[经度|东经]]140°以东的预警范围内，克里斯蒂也是本季持续时间最长的热带气旋。

== 形成 ==
{{storm path|Kristy 2006 track.png}}
8月13日，一股[[东风波|东风波]]离开西非海岸向西移动，系统内有大规模的下层云系漩涡，用了一个多星期时间经过大西洋和加勒比海，于8月22日穿越[[中美洲|中美洲]]<ref name="tcr" />。8月29日，系统的组织结构有所改善，内部有大规模[[低气压|低气压区]]和[[雷暴|雷暴]]活动存在<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Brown | author2 = Stewart | date = 2006-08-29 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>。对流持续存在并进一步组织，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]8月30日凌晨0点将位于[[下加利福尼亚半岛|下加利福尼亚半岛]]最南端西南方向约970公里海域的系统归类为[[2006年太平洋飓风季|2006年太平洋飓风季]]第十二{{lang|en|E}}号热带低气压<ref name="tcr" />。

成为热带气旋后，低气压遇到少量东向[[风切变|风切变]]，导致环流以西的对流出现扭曲。不过，气象机构认为外部环境总体有利于系统强化，预计低气压会达到风速每小时85公里的最高强度后再减弱。<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Rhome | author2 = Franklin | date = 2006-08-30 | title = Tropical Depression Twelve-E Special Discussion One | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-11 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.001.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002121206/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.001.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>气旋沿[[高压脊|高压脊]]的南部边缘缓慢向西北方向移动，并在环流中心上空的对流得以增长后迅速增强成热带风暴。风切变这时已经变得非常少，系统行经洋面的[[海面温度|水温]]也很高，预计风暴会迅速强化至飓风标准。<ref name="disc2">{{cite report | author = Stewart | date = 2006-08-30 | title = Tropical Storm Kristy Discussion Two | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-11 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.002.shtml? | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002121210/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.002.shtml }}</ref>到了8月30日晚，对流已经逐渐将环流中心包裹起来，风暴中的[[风眼|眼状特征]]时隐时现<ref name="disc4">{{cite report | author = Pasch | date = 2006-08-30 | title = Tropical Storm Kristy Discussion Four | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-11 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.004.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002121212/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.004.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>。克里斯蒂继续组织，在成形约30小时后于8月31日清晨升级成飓风<ref name="tcr" />。达到飓风标准约6小时后，卫星图像上已经可以看到明显的眼状特征，估计飓风已在[[下加利福尼亚州|下加利福尼亚州]]最南端的西南方向约880公里海域达到持续风速每小时130公里的最高强度<ref name="tcr" />。不过，从卫星获得的数据估算，克里斯蒂有可能是风力时速达170公里的二级飓风，也有可能只达到热带风暴标准<ref name="disc7">{{cite report | author = Franklin | date = 2006-08-31 | title = Hurricane Kristy Discussion Seven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-11 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.007.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002121222/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.007.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>。

== 逐渐减弱及消亡 ==
接下来，位于克里斯蒂以东的强劲[[2006年飓风约翰|飓风约翰]]的[[外流_(气象学)|外流]]导致风切变有所增长<ref name="tcr" />，同时，克里斯蒂行经洋面的水温也有所降低，风暴在卫星图像上开始变得模糊不清。与此同时，转向气流有所减弱，气旋接下来的动向也难以确认，美国国家飓风中心预计飓风会缓慢西进并在4天内逐渐消散。不过，也有其他多个[[热带气旋预测模型|飓风模型]]预计克里斯蒂会向西南方向移动，还有两个模型预测风暴会同飓风约翰发生[[藤原效应|藤原效应]]，最终克里斯蒂会被约翰吸收。<ref>{{cite report | author = Beven | date = 2006-09-01 | title = Hurricane Kristy Discussion Nine | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-11 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002121226/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.009.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.009.shtml? | display-authors = etal | deadurl = no }}</ref>9月1日，飓风降级成热带风暴<ref name="tcr" />，并且减弱速度还因干燥空气侵入而加快<ref>{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002121235/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.011.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.011.shtml? | author1 = Mainelli | author2 = Avila | deadurl = no | date = 2006-09-01 | title = Tropical Storm Kristy Discussion Eleven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-12 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>。受北侧高压脊增强影响，气旋转向东南<ref name="tcr" />。9月2日，环流从对流中暴露出来，美国国家飓风中心预计系统会在24小时内退化成残留低气压<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Fiorino | author2 = Avila | date = 2006-09-02 | title = Tropical Storm Kristy Discussion Fifteen | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-12 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.015.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002121248/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.015.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>。当晚，克里斯蒂又降级成热带低气压<ref name="tcr" />。

[[File:12E_Kristy_20060830.jpg|right]]

到9月3日时，热带低气压克里斯蒂内已经连续近18小时没有持续存在的深层对流<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Roberts | author2 = Beven | date = 2006-09-03 | title = Tropical Depression Kristy Discussion Seventeen | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002121251/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.017.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.017.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-12 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>。但过了一段时间，其中心围绕的雷暴又有增长，还逐渐发展出浅层眼状特征<ref>{{cite report | author = Stewart | date = 2006-09-03 | title = Tropical Depression Kristy Discussion Eighteen | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002121259/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.018.shtml | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-11-12 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.018.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>。对流沿环流的西部边缘持续，估计气旋在首度降级成热带低气压约24小时后又再度增强成热带风暴<ref name="tcr" /><ref>{{cite report | author1 = Fiorino | author2 = Franklin | date = 2006-09-03 | title = Tropical Storm Kristy Discussion Twenty | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002121301/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.020.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.020.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。与此同时，克里斯开始稳步向西南方向前进。随着持续存在的风切变令对流减弱，令中心同雷暴完全分离，风暴的这次重新增强过程只持续了很短的时间。9月4日，气旋再度降级成热带低气压，气象机构估计系统很快就会消散，但也有可能随间歇性的对流爆发而重新发展<ref>{{cite report | author = Avila | date = 2006-09-04 | title = Tropical Depression Kristy Discussion Twenty-Two | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002121309/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.022.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.022.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>。9月5日，对流出现爆发并围绕中心持续存在，确保克里斯蒂第3次升级成热带风暴。风切变这时已经减少，风暴转向西进，行经洋面水温偏高，预计克里斯蒂会在接下来5天内保持热带风暴强度<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Blake | author2 = Stewart | date = 2006-09-05 | title = Tropical Storm Kristy Discussion Twenty-Seven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-12 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.027.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002121320/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.027.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-10-02 }}</ref>。保持热带风暴强度向西移动期间，克里斯蒂的雷暴活动一度表现出逐渐组织成联结带的迹象，美国国家飓风中心预计气旋很可能会有进一步强化，风力时速有望达到95公里<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Blake | author2 = Stewart | date = 2006-09-05 | title = Tropical Storm Kristy Discussion Twenty-Eight | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151006044130/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.028.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.028.shtml? | accessdate = 2015-11-12 | archivedate = 2015-10-06 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。然后，雷暴活动在9月6日大幅消减<ref>{{cite report | author = Beven | date = 2006-09-06 | title = Tropical Storm Kristy Discussion Thirty | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151006045129/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.030.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.030.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-06 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，这主要是因为受到干燥空气的侵蚀<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Roberts | author2 = Franklin | date = 2006-09-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151006101435/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.032.shtml | title = Tropical Depression Kristy Discussion Thirty-Two | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-12 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.032.shtml? | archivedate = 2015-10-06 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，气旋随即第3次也是最后一次弱化成热带低气压<ref name="tcr" />。气象机构的其中一份预测认为，克里斯蒂会行进至[[经度|西经]]140°以西，进入[[中太平洋飓风中心|中太平洋飓风中心]]预警责任区<ref>{{cite report | author = Pasch | date = 2006-09-07 | title = Tropical Depression Kristy Discussion Thirty-Three | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151006064350/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.033.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.033.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2015-11-12 | archivedate = 2015-10-06 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。但低气压实际上未能维持组织结构这么长时间<ref>{{cite report | author1 = Berg | author2 = Avila | date = 2006-09-08 | title = Tropical Depression Kristy Discussion Thirty-Seven | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.037.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151006062632/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2006/ep12/ep122006.discus.037.shtml | accessdate = 2015-11-12 | archivedate = 2015-10-06 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，只过了两天就于9月8日退化成残留低气压。低气压转向西南，于9月9日在[[夏威夷岛|夏威夷岛]]东南方向约2400公里海域退化成东风波，这里已是[[下加利福尼亚半岛|下加利福尼亚半岛]]最南端的西南方向约2600公里外。<ref name="tcr" />系统残留继续西进，气象部门一度以为东风波又在中太平洋发展成第二{{lang|en|C}}号热带低气压，但经过飓风季后的重新分析，中太平洋飓风中心认定两个天气系统间没有继承关系<ref name="cphc">{{cite report | author = Central Pacific Hurricane Center | year = 2008 | title = Mission Statement | accessdate = 2015-11-12 | url = http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/summaries/2006.php | archivedate = 2008-01-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080103013712/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/summaries/2006.php | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>。

